  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening STI policy and governance</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The activity aims at strengthening national and regional STI systems and governance, through providing advice and guidance for the development, review and implementation of evidence-based, inclusive and gender-responsive STI policies. UNESCO will provide new methodological framework and guidelines for working in the field of STI policy by streamlining the approach in line with the Agenda 2030 and the SDGs. The activity will focus on the development and use of new UNESCO tools, as means for STI governance and policy implementation.</narrative>
